resources.string: Ungasebenzisa amaswishi ukuze ukhethe izinto, uskrole, uhlobo, nokunye.

Amaswishi angakusiza ukuthi ulawule idivayisi yakho ye-Android uma kunzima ukusebenzisana ngokuqondile nesikrini esithintwayo. Iswishi ingaxhunywa ngaphandle kudivayisi yakho, njengekhibhodi noma inkinobho enkulu.
